metadata.description:
Frédéric
11/27/2013
nft 1/1
7559*5670px
Max resolution

Photography Masterpiece for the visual communication of the "Manoir de Paris" for its Escape Game Christmas season 2013/2014.
Inspired by "la Liberté guidant le peuple" - "Liberty guiding the people" by Eugène Delacroix in 1830 and "The Nightmare before Christmas" directed by Henry Selick & Tim Burton released in 1993.
